      { "@type": "Question", "name": "How much does central heating installation cost in Formby?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "A full central heating installation in Formby starts from £3,500 for a smaller property. Larger Formby homes with multi-zone systems typically fall between £5,500 and £8,000 depending on number of radiators, zones and whether underfloor circuits are included. All prices are confirmed at a free written fixed-price site survey." } },
