      { "@type": "Question", "name": "Can you install underfloor heating connected to the central heating system in Formby?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. Wet underfloor heating circuits connected to the system boiler are common in Formby kitchen extensions and renovation projects. We design and install underfloor circuits alongside the main radiator system at the free survey. G3 qualified engineers ensure unvented cylinder integration is also correctly specified where applicable." } },
