        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Multi-zone system design where applicable</strong><p>For properties with 10 or more radiators, we design a properly zoned system at the free survey. Zone valves, motorised valves and independent thermostats for each zone included.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Underfloor circuits where specified</strong><p>Wet underfloor circuits connected to the system boiler, with dedicated zone control and manifold. For kitchen extensions, utility rooms and ground floor renovation areas.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Full radiator set designed for each room</strong><p>We calculate the correct radiator output for every room. Every room gets the right amount of heat, sized correctly for the room's dimensions and heat loss.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Smart multi-zone controls and thermostat</strong><p>Nest or Hive smart multi-zone thermostats installed and set up for properties with zone control. Independent zone schedules from your phone. Required under Boiler Plus regulations for all new installations.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Magnetic system filter and inhibitor</strong><p>Magnetic filter fitted and system dosed with inhibitor to BS 7593 standard. A warranty condition for all major boiler manufacturers and essential for long-term system health.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Unvented cylinder specification and installation where required</strong><p>For multi-bathroom Formby properties. G3 qualified installation and commissioning. Cylinder sized for the property's hot water demand. Annual inspection certification available on the same visit as the annual boiler service.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Full commissioning and system balance</strong><p>Every radiator balanced. Every zone and underfloor circuit commissioned. Full heating and hot water cycle run across all zones before we leave.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Gas Safe certificate, Benchmark certificate and 12-month workmanship guarantee</strong><p>Both certificates issued on the day of completion. Boiler warranty registered with the manufacturer on your behalf. 12-month workmanship guarantee on all installation work.</p></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


