          <div class="pf-duration-time">7-10<br><span style="font-size:0.9rem;">days</span></div>
          <div><strong>Large renovation or extension project. Multi-zone plus underfloor circuits.</strong><p>System boiler, multiple zones, underfloor circuits in extension areas, unvented cylinder for multi-bathroom properties. Complex system designs planned fully at the free survey. Price and timeline confirmed before any work begins.</p></div>
