      <p class="pf-sub">Gas Safe registered. G3 qualified. Multi-zone specialists. Underfloor circuit expertise. Free fixed-price survey. No sub-contractors. All Formby L37 postcodes.</p>
      <div class="pf-why-grid">
        <div class="pf-why-item"><h3>Multi-Zone System Design</h3><p>We design multi-zone heating systems for Formby's larger properties at the free survey. Zone valves, independent thermostats, smart controls. The right system for a large property, not a combi installed where the old boiler was.</p></div>
        <div class="pf-why-item"><h3>Underfloor Circuit Expertise</h3><p>Wet underfloor circuits connected to the system boiler for kitchen extensions and renovation areas. Designed and installed as part of the full central heating installation. G3 qualified engineers ensure the complete system including the cylinder is correctly specified.</p></div>
        <div class="pf-why-item"><h3>Free Survey and Fixed Price</h3><p>We visit your Formby property, assess every factor including zone design, underfloor circuit requirements and cylinder sizing, then provide a written fixed-price quote. No surprises on invoice day for complex multi-zone jobs.</p></div>
        <div class="pf-why-item"><h3>G3 Qualified for Unvented Cylinder Work</h3><p>Our engineers hold G3 qualification for unvented cylinder installation, inspection and certification. Legally required for this work. We design, install and certify the complete system in a single project.</p></div>
        <div class="pf-why-item"><h3>Our Own Gas Safe Engineers</h3><p>Every installation carried out by our own directly employed Gas Safe and G3 qualified engineers. Never a sub-contractor. The same professionals throughout the full installation on multi-day complex jobs.</p></div>
        <div class="pf-why-item"><h3>Boiler Plus Compliant</h3><p>All installations meet Boiler Plus regulations and current Building Regulations. A compliant installation protects your investment. Particularly important for Formby properties where renovation quality affects resale value.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


